Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal Fernandez...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:14.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby place you under arrest for the \Ncrime of high treason against the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:53.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:02.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Guild for Only One.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:09.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal has lost his memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't remember a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:16.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By clause 13 of the criminal code, \Nthat is not a valid defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:22.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can release them from the runes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:24.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I have no intention of resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:36.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never was able to remember you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:44.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly sorry, Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:48.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She tells me that long \Nago, she was saved by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:53.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:58.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know how much suffering \NI must have caused all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:03.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But to hear that I saved \Nsomeone makes me glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:08.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:18.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:37.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for me to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal is going away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:48.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal, finally awakened from \Nhis long nightmare, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:54.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I just let him be shut \Nup in the darkness yet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there nothing left you wish to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:09.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty much guaranteed you'll be \Nexecuted or given life without parole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never see another human face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:18.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't takin' him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:29.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're from the Council!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:32.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're takin' him back with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:47.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Leave me be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Restrain them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:04:59.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:04.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no stopping Natsu now, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:08.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It don't sit right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:10.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He helped defend you from Nirvana!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:14.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't got even one word of thanks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is truth to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is unjust to arrest a man like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It pains me to say it, but if that man \Nis taken away, Erza-san will be saddened!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me if anyone gets hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:34.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't take Jellal with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:41.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't leave Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to stay by her side! For her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:50.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So come here! We stand with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're allies, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:55.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For obstructing government officials \Nand aiding in the escape of a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:13.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's far enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for the fuss we've caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:23.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... will take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:41.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:00.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the color of your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:15.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:57.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Erza go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave her alone for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:04.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:12.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To hear that I saved someone makes me glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal Fernandez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's hard to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:34.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That name's gonna tie my tongue in knots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:39.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name, "Wally Buchanan", \Nseems hard to remember, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:42.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just plain Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:50.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:55.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:57.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:03.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let's name you "Erza Scarlet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Name you"? Don't just \Ngo naming other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:14.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza Scarlet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:27.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet. The color of your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:34.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:44.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That morning's dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,was painted a beautiful scarlet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the likes of which I had never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:54.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the color of Erza's hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it was warm, and passionate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:07.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If she could only lift her face, a beautiful \Nsky would be spread out before her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If she could only lift her face...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:43.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I'm far cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire village here is part of the guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so clothing production \Nis a thriving business!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some kind of Nirvit traditional sewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:58.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it... Maybe it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:04.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't realize that the guild was \Nall descendants of the Nirvit, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm the only one who joined afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:11.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, won't you try them \Non? They're really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:24.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Wendy... When did \NCaitshelter join the League of Guilds?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:29.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for being blunt, \Nbut until this mission began,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had not even heard your guild's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, neither had I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:41.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My guild must really be one \Nof the more obscure ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:45.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? Everyone is waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:51.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lamia Scale...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Wendy and Carla.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:12:03.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have done well in defeating \NOracion Seis and stopping Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:07.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a representative for the \Nlocal League of Guilds,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Robaul, say job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabula!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:19.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was our pleasure, Master Robaul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:24.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight with Oracion Seis was \None fierce battle after the next!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:29.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was not a single easy battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the bonds between us allies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:36.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,led us on the path to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:39.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:42.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh sure, just take all the \Ngood parts for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he even fight anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:51.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You two did well yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jura-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:55.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to throw a party now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:12:59.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:00.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...will join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...will join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:07.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:09.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And off go the clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:11.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Everyone from Caitshelter, join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:55.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:14:01.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly sorry about hiding \Nour legacy as Nirvit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:07.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined the mood to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We really don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:10.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I don't mind either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:24.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please listen carefully \Nto what I am about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:35.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To start, we are not the \Ndescendants of the Nirvit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:41.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Nirvit themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:48.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,400 years ago, it was I who created Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:49.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:51.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:54.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,400 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:07.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,400 years ago, in order to stop the \Nwar that was raging across the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:13.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I created Nirvana, a magic that \Ninverts light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:20.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana became our country,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:25.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and, for a time, we realized peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:28.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:36.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great power will, without fail, give \Nrise to a great power opposing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:44.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As much as Nirvana changed darkness for \Nlight, Nirvana itself became wrapped in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was to maintain balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:55.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was impossible to change people's \Npersonalities to light without limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:16:00.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As light rises to oppose the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:04.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so does darkness rise to oppose \Nthe light, without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:07.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:28.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness lost from the various \Npeoples came back upon us Nirvit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:30.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:46.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We killed each other... \NUntil no one was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:57.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:07.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at this point, \Nthat's not exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:15.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My physical body has long perished... I am \Nwhat you might call a spectral form now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:26.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, a weak ghost trying to \Natone for his sins of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:36.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched over Nirvana for 400 years until \Nsomeone appeared who would be able to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:45.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...my role is finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:55.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:07.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magna! Pepel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:12.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:14.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for deceiving you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:34.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the members of the guild \Nare illusions created by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Illusions with their own personalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:43.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:54.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...lived alone in these \Nruins, protecting Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:19:00.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,7 years ago, a single boy came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, take care of this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:15.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't turn down the request of \Nthat boy and his fierce, honest eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:21.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I had promised \Nmyself I would stay alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:25.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:35.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was taking me to a guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is a guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:40.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Wizard's Guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:42.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabula!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:45.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Try going outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:49.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have friends waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:55.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I also created an illusory family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:58.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The guild was created all for Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:04.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bask, Naoki, don't you disappear too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:11.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, Carla... You no longer \Nneed a foster family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:22.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have real friends now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your future... has only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:41.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:47.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, truly, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:52.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave Wendy and Carla in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:20.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:22:06.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bury the pain of losing your loved \Nones... into the arms of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:17.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:20.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:58.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it's been a while \Nsince we've been back to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.85,0:23:59.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.67,0:24:01.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can finally take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.57,0:24:03.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it doesn't look like we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:06.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there's a person that saw a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:07.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:10.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that dragon be Igneel?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:14.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's the Dragon that Wendy \Nand Carla are looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:16.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Call of the Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:20.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... What was the name of the \Ndragon they were looking for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.94,0:24:23.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it's "Wendine".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I think you're mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:26.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
